    <Ritual>
        <Nerangs id="ritualNerangs">
            <ab>YR0.3 Var. a (mss. 300, 355, 360, 370):</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                ō gāh ātrawaxšān šudan war ō ī ādurgāh ud barsom ud hamāg sāzišn xūb nigerīdan ud tarsāgāhīhā menīdan <em>aṣ̌əm vōhū</em> sē guftan</ab>  
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                He should go to the place of the <em>ātrawaxš</em> facing the <em>ātaxšgāh</em> and <em>barsom</em>. He should gaze carefully at all implements and think respectfully.
                He shoul recite three <em>aṣ̌əm vohū</em>.</ab>
            <ab>YR0.3 Var. b (ms. 365):</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                pīš. ātaš. īštāδan. <em>nəmsitē ātaraš mazdā̊ ahurahe haodā̊ mazšta yazata xšnaoϑra ahurahe mazdā̊ aṣ̌əm vōhū</em> sə̄</ab>
            <ab class="ab_indent">
                "He should stay before the fire. (He recites): <em>nəmsitē ātarš mazdå ahurahē haodå mazšta yazata xšnaōθra ahurahe mazdå</em> and three <em>aṣ̌əm vōhū</em>."</ab>
        </Nerangs>
    </Ritual>
